{"tid":1407933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8.5 全民運動日？","createTime":"2019-08-04T16:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:28:43.000Z","uid":163118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f0189192e2d87a4f3921bb701fcb8dd86f5e108","tid":1407933,"uid":163118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"大家都知啦連登係一個鼓吹市民多做運動嘅健康討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果聽日啲人帶住自己嘅足球啊籃球啊排球啊各種球類去搭地鐵去其他地方做運動 實會佔左車廂部分空間搞到好鬼逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令到少咗人上班列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />甚至閂唔到門就唔係幾好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以建議喜愛做運動嘅人可以帶球類出門 但千萬要記得帶埋波針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣做完運動離開嘅陣可以放氣 然後放入袋輕輕鬆鬆去集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可唔可行啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca6230a3768f471f654a8ac03f24885072db4e8","tid":1407933,"uid":163118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e1e20b9c7d6126b742b8587707a76150ceb30e","tid":1407933,"uid":267235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該入一入黎幫手推post</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/14